window.bookSummaryJSON = "<p><b>Some skills you never lose. Killing is one of them.</b></p> <p>Matthew Riker keeps to himself, doesn't cause trouble, and never talks about his past. But after a chance encounter with a woman and a small child on the run, Riker will have to make a choice: use his hard-won skills to protect two innocent victims, or stay in the safety of his quiet life.</p> <p>What follows is an adrenaline-soaked thrill ride that will take Riker on a cross-country chase, through the seedy underbelly of a New York criminal empire, and into the darkest places of the human heart.</p> <p><b>Fans of John Wick, Jack Reacher, and Jason Bourne...get ready to meet Matthew Riker.</b></p> <p>Includes a bonus novella from the Matthew Riker series, <i>No Loose Ends</i>.</p>"; 
